response.overview: It's DELTA's final match in Australian wrestling, Brother vs. Sister as she faces her own brother in a No Holds Barred match!  Elsewhere on the card, Chris Basso and Matt Hayter meet each other one on one for the first time in 5 years for Basso's RCW Grand Championship  The C4 ABSOLUTE Grand Prix kicks off with Snaxx vs. Vincent Di Maria and Sigma vs. Zak Sabbath.  Plus Thorn Enterprises, Kings of Ruin, Cadie Tre, Nick Armstrong and more in action!
response.title: RCW Heavy Is The Crown 2024
